dct_title_s: India Proper : or the Empire of the Great Mogul agreeable to Modern History
dct_description_sm: Cartographic Details: Scale [1:14,000,000]. Imprint derived from the atlas in which the map was issued. Numbered 36. Shows boundaries, rivers, roads and settlements. London meridian. Relief shown pictorially. Dimensions: 26 x 20 centimeters
